title: King Diamond And Black Rose - A Night At Rehearsal
description:
King Diamond and Black Rose "20 Years Ago A Night of Rehearsal" CD. 1980 recordings by King Diamond and his band Black Rose, which he was in prior to joining Mercyful Fate and making heavy metal history! This is pre-falsetto King Diamond here and the band is playing a high energy brand of Deep Purple styled 70s hard rock complete with organ/moog! This is really for fans of 70s hard rock as there&#039;s a little metal in the sound, but not much.

1. Locked Up In The Snow.
2. Holy Mountain Lights.
3. Crazy Tonights.
4. Virgin.
5. Kill For Fun.
6. The End.
7. Road Life.
8. Soul Overture.
9. Doctor Cranium.
10. Disgrace.
11. I Need Blood.
12. Radar Love.
